    <p>
      Our Summer Workshop is a unique residential programme in Odissi basics as developed and practised at Nrityagram, which also brings to students a compact experience of our philosophy of “practising art as a way of life”. 
    </p>
    <p>
      Odissi will be taught by <a href="/surupa" class="bodylink">Surupa Sen</a> (Artistic Director Nrityagram Dance Ensemble) and <a href="/pavithra" class="bodylink">Pavithra Reddy</a> (Director of Educational and Outreach Programmes), both of whom have been studying and practising at Nrityagram for the past 34 years.
    </p>
    <p>
      Yoga sessions will be led by Jaya Chakraborty who has over 2 decades of training and teaching. In 2013 Jaya founded The Practice Room, Bangalore.
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
